title: New Philips Shaver series 9000
description:
Do you want the best shave you have ever had and to repeat that experience every time you shave? It’s time to get acquainted with the Philips Shaver series 9000. 

These are the advantages of shaving with Philips S9000:
• V-Track Precision Blades to have the best shaving experience
• Unique close shave thanks to the contour detect technology of this electric shaver
• Personal comfort settings to have the best mode to shave; Sensitive, Normal or Fast shaving
• With AquaTec wet & dry you can use this electric shaver in the shower and also lubricate with foam and gel
